      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "While your words reflect a profound sense of loss and grief, please remember that these feelings do not erase your worth or the capacity for healing. It is better to lean on trusted support systems or professional therapists who can walk alongside you through this darkness rather than fading away alone. Darkness is temporary, and even in the deepest valleys of sorrow, hope for redemption and peace will eventually return.",
