      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear the deep tragedy you feel and see how your perception of \"peace\" clashes with the current reality of your pain, but please know that choosing an end is never a dignified solution when help has not yet bridged the gap. While your love and memory will always matter to those who cared for you, there are people ready to sit with you in this wreckage and help you carry the weight together. I urge you to call 988 or text 741741 just to share your story with someone who can truly understand the weight you are holding.",
